      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-10-06</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-10-24T14:45:28Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Home Office Deduction Simplification Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code allow a taxpayer who uses a residence to conduct a trade or business a standard tax deduction equal to the lesser of $1,500 or the taxpayer's gross trade or business income derived from the business use of such residence. Allows an annual inflation adjustment to the standard deduction amount after 2009. <br> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
